story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_01: According to Looker, Cyrus should be in this cave.
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_02:
Yeah. But Looker must’ve been tired, because he
went right back to sleep after telling us!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_03: From here on out, it’s up to us.
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_04: I’m counting on you, too, Sophocles.
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_05:
Sure! I know we can get Cyrus to understand us
if we can talk to him!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_06: Darkrai?! That must mean Cyrus really is here!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_08: Oh no! We got too close to Darkrai!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_09: N-no... I can’t...keep my eyes open...
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_11: No, let’s go into the nightmare!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_13: If Cyrus is already in Darkrai’s nightmare...
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_14: then I think we have to go to sleep, too.
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_15: I see. Let’s go for it, then.
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_16: Bring it on! We’ll do it for Master Cyrus!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_17: Y-yeah! I can do it, too!
story_teamgalactic_02_09000/2401_1201_18: I’ll see you soon...in our dreams...
